  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1263792/" class="title-link">挺好看的</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1263792"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1376750/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1376750-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1376750/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">didi</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-12-20"
      class="main-meta">2007-12-20 17:54:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1263792_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  挺好看的书，写的扣人心弦，张弛有度。  竹千代的童年真是跌宕起伏，提心吊胆，能在那么个年代活下来，然后树立起自己的旗帜，可以和他相比的恐怕只有那个犬千代了。  开始看前十章感觉一般，越往后看，越好看，尤其是於大离开冈崎之后，越来越好看。  简单地说，第一集据说了...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1263792_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1263792_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
